{"tid":1648414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「世異則事異，事異則備變」 每日讀韓非","createTime":"2019-10-12T07:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:09:48.000Z","uid":63328,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"838714368edc70953c390b98a4f931a1622d8d7b","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">世異則事異，事異則備變</div></span><br />\n時代唔同，事情就唔一樣。<br />\n事情唔一樣，就要準備應變啦，香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTkavdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTkavdo.png&h=cb4b99e0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n盡量每日譯一段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf20f700086243d5699558b4045fc88686815c58","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>【原文】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>上</strong>古之世，人民少而禽獸眾，人民不勝禽獸蟲蛇。有聖人作，搆木為巢以避羣害，而民悅之，使王天下，號之曰有巢氏。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>民</strong>食果、蓏、蜯、蛤，腥、臊、惡、臭，而傷害腹胃，民多疾病。有聖人作，鑽燧取火，以化腥臊，而民說之，使王天下，號之曰燧人氏。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中</strong>古之世，天下大水，而鯀、禹決瀆。近古之世，桀、紂暴亂，而湯、武征伐。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今</strong>有搆木鑽燧於夏后氏之世者，必為鯀、禹笑矣；有決瀆於殷、周之世者，必為湯、武笑矣。然則今有美堯、舜、禹、湯、武之道於當今之世者，必為新聖笑矣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>是</strong>以聖人不期循古，不法常行，論世之事，因為之備。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>宋</strong>人有耕田者，田中有株，兔走觸株，折頸而死。因釋其耒而守株，冀復得兔，兔不可復得，而身為宋國笑。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今</strong>欲以先王之政，治當世之民，皆守株之類也。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 《韓非子》五蠹"},{"pid":"6fd5180cbe64b1cacbf4b54c4c48151e9662b025","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>【錯譯】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>是</strong>咁的。好耐之前，人少而何君堯多，人民搞唔掂班蛇蟲鼠蟻、元朗鄉親。後來有聖人出現，教民眾用木起屋避禽獸，人民服從佢既領導，推佢做王，就成為有巢氏。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>又</strong>，大家食水果蔬菜海鮮獸肉，又腥又臭又唔衛生，上吐下瀉，成日作病。又有聖人出現，教人鑽木取火BBQ，自此唔再食生肉，人民服從佢既領導，推佢做王，就成為燧人氏。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中</strong>古時候，全世界水災，鯀、禹教你疏導洪水。近古時候，夏桀、商紂癡撚線，就有商湯、周武推翻暴政。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不</strong>過，如果有巢氏喺鯀、禹既時代教鑽木取火，就實畀人笑啦。又如果有人喺商、周時代教疏導洪水，都肯定會被人恥笑。所以如果而家有人教你堯、舜、禹、湯、武既治世方法，佢肯定係傻架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所</strong>以，真正有料既人，唔會盲從以往做法，亦唔會盲從現今規範。而係會根據現時情況，因時制宜。咁先叫有料。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3ahUGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3ahUGv.png&h=1feb3fae&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<strong>有</strong>無聽過守株待兔呀？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以</strong>前宋國有個農夫，農田裡有棵樹，有隻白癡兔仔撞左落棵樹度，死左。就係咁，佢唔再耕田，日日喺棵樹隔離等兔仔撞樹，最後咪成為成語囉。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所</strong>以你想用1989年既方法去治理今日既民眾，都係同守株待兔一樣智障架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450148d4795e198de6779e51a7518b21bbf545cd","tid":1648414,"uid":236281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYXcJBO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYXcJBO.jpg&h=b5f3ec88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64b9af4f9ce3d203511a2cc8c8e129ec58dda3eb","tid":1648414,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68c5c0e96be70a960ca3258949038fd9ac1ce7b8","tid":1648414,"uid":73406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"好耐無見壽桃巴<br />\n雖然你唔識我"},{"pid":"5daec6a6904e463135df6912011ee1b45888a8ec","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68c5c0e96be70a960ca3258949038fd9ac1ce7b8","tid":1648414,"uid":73406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"好耐無見壽桃巴<br />\n雖然你唔識我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:23:22.000Z","msg":"你好巴打，我同探長都轉左場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@lihkgheavytaste\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lihkgheavytaste&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=d5983113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@lihkgheavytaste</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@deliver546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40deliver546&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=aa8a0d07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@deliver546</a>"},{"pid":"e0c705d98dbdff60e681f217dd18a245174d5a2d","tid":1648414,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n香港人真 &middot; 反抗！！！<br />\n<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669】＜\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669】＜</a></div></ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"0d00be7189b0e6f66f1c82da14d93c901fabd15d","tid":1648414,"uid":6005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇文言文，巴打譯得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca9f386ee442aaafe695266f9e43a02c81433da","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yABhc99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyABhc99.png&h=188e6753&s={SIZE}\" /></div> <br />\n<br />\n事因於世，而備適於事。<br />\n備適於事。你既準備應該要針對情況，唔係鳩黎。<br />\n<br />\n洞窟用長劍，就係不備適於事。"},{"pid":"3c28134bd33f3a014ad772ee660a187865342d04","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>【原文】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>古</strong>者丈夫不耕，草木之實足食也；婦人不織，禽獸之皮足衣也。不事力而養足，人民少而財有餘，故民不爭。是以厚賞不行，重罰不用，而民自治。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今</strong>人有五子不為多，子又有五子，大父未死而有二十五孫。是以人民眾而貨財寡，事力勞而供養薄，故民爭，雖倍賞累罰而不免於亂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>堯</strong>之王天下也，茅茨不翦，采椽不斲，糲粢之食，藜藿之羹；冬曰麑裘，夏日葛衣，雖監門之服養，不虧於此矣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>禹</strong>之王天下也，身執耒臿，以為民先，股無胈，脛不生毛，雖臣虜之勞，不苦於此矣。以是言之，夫古之讓天子者，是去監門之養，而離臣虜之勞也，古傳天下而不足多也。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>今</strong>之縣令，一日身死，子孫累絜駕，故人重之。是以人之於讓也，輕辭古之天子，難去今之縣令者，薄厚之實異也。夫山居而谷汲者，膢臘而相遺以水；澤居苦水者，買庸而決竇。故饑歲之春，幼弟不饟；穰歲之秋，疏客必食。非疏骨肉愛過客也，多少之實異也。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>是</strong>以古之易財，非仁也，財多也；今之爭奪，非鄙也，財寡也。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>輕</strong>辭天子，非高也，勢薄也；重爭士橐，非下也，權重也。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>故</strong>聖人議多少，論薄厚為之政。故罰薄不為慈，誅嚴不為戾，稱俗而行也。故事因於世，而備適於事。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 《韓非子》五蠹"},{"pid":"599b0644dcbdf39c709cff5f7267ea81d8158274","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>【錯譯】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>以</strong>前無人耕田，因為摘野果都夠食。女人亦唔會織衣，因為獸皮已經夠著。民眾生活充足，人少而財富多，所以個個客氣禮讓。唔洗重賞亦無須重罰，大家自己搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>而</strong>家一個人生五個都唔算多，五個又各自再生五個，老豆未死就已經有廿五個孫。人多物質少，OT多人工奀，所以大家都爭。即使重賞重罰，社會都會混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>堯</strong>做大佬嗰陣，住茅屋食野菜。冬天著鹿皮，夏日穿布衣。同守城門嗰條粉腸差唔多待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>禹</strong>做大佬嗰陣，以身作則，自己攞住鋤頭耕田，屎忽白滑、大髀無毛（？！）。同做奴僕一樣咁低賤。所以佢地成日玩禪讓，基本上即係俄羅斯練膽大法，大家快快手傳炸彈，唔想再做下賤野，唔係真係咩咁高尚。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCHcMwR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCHcMwR.png&h=520beda7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而</strong>家即使只係做個縣令，第日死左，子子孫孫都可以繼續攞福利，咁大家咪爭住做囉。所以講到讓呢，古時唔做天子易，今日唔做縣令難，講到底都只係福利待遇差別姐。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>住</strong>深山而要喺谷底攞水既山民，大時大節係會互相送水。住喺水災區既人，會專門請人掘水道排洪。饑旱既時候，自己細佬都可以餓死。豐收既年頭，秋香會派野食畀華安。哩啲唔係厚疏賤親，而係擁有多與少既問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所</strong>以以前啲人中意些牙，唔係佢地仁慈，只係佢地富有。而家啲人爭奪，唔係佢地賤格，而係DLLM 窮呀。古時禪讓唔做天子，只係因為天子唔係位高權重，仲要無人聽佢話。而家連做縣令都要爭，因為縣令唔係低下階層，仲有權有勢呀。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>真</strong>正領導者施政要考慮埋多少、厚薄。罰得少，唔代表仁慈。罰得嚴，唔代表暴戾。<br />\n「事因於世，備適於事」，就係要考慮現實環境先作出決定。"},{"pid":"4d005779f683f213a40af7674eeeb8778cf8a72f","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64b9af4f9ce3d203511a2cc8c8e129ec58dda3eb","tid":1648414,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"李家樹我記得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1e3255b9c73b86dfe12f0ac7b4676f47aa5b94","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"abb917e45f5da5d8aa086c77dee5de54c23ea430","tid":1648414,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d005779f683f213a40af7674eeeb8778cf8a72f","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64b9af4f9ce3d203511a2cc8c8e129ec58dda3eb","tid":1648414,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"李家樹我記得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"我邊個po留過名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5ca73277d697d53aa7199c2614345efcd5b30d","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqzK0e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqzK0e6.png&h=6efb394d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n「事異則備變」。獅鳥就係時勢做神獸既體現。</div>"},{"pid":"e8e5d394c583be6ece640b18a30f19970d9e72bb","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>【原文】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>古</strong>者，文王處豐、鎬之間，地方百里，行仁義而懷西戎，遂王天下。徐偃王處漢東，地方五百里，行仁義，割地而朝者三十有六國。荊文王恐其害己也，舉兵伐徐，遂滅之。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>故</strong>文王行仁義而王天下，偃王行仁義而喪其國，是仁義用於古而不用於今也。故曰：「世異則事異」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當</strong>舜之時，有苗不服，禹將伐之。舜曰：「不可。上德不厚而行武，非道也。」乃修教三年，執干戚舞，有苗乃服。共工之戰，鐵銛距者及乎敵，鎧甲不堅者傷乎體。是干戚用於古不用於今也。故曰：「事異則備變」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>上古競於道德，中世逐於智謀，當今爭於氣力。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>齊</strong>將攻魯，魯使子貢說之。齊人曰：「子言非不辯也，吾所欲者土地也，非斯言所謂也。」遂舉兵伐魯，去門十里以為界。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>故</strong>偃王仁義而徐亡，子貢辯智而魯削。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以</strong>是言之，夫仁義、辯智，非所以持國也。去偃王之仁，息子貢之智，循徐、魯之力，使敵萬乘，則齊、荊之欲不得行於二國矣。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 《韓非子》五蠹"},{"pid":"04bfe34f1c1eb3a804bf859517cdc073fb15f7fc","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>【錯譯】</strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuZyTCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuZyTCN.jpg&h=91db823d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(圖為西伯侯姬昌，即係周文王，Ikea 肉丸意粉既忠實支持者)</div><br />\n<br />\n是咁的。以前周文王喺大西北，西安嗰頭起家，得一百里地。不過佢講仁義，連大西北啲野人都服佢，所以最後咪做到大佬囉。<br />\n<br />\n又，徐偃王喺漢東做老細，有成五百里地。佢學足周文王嗰套，走去講仁義，有成三十六個國家甘願做佢契弟。楚文王擔心佢愈做愈大，就直接派兵打佢，最後滅埋徐國，吹咩。<br />\n<br />\n你睇，周文王行仁義而得天下，徐偃王行仁義而收皮。「仁義」而家係行唔通啦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">哩啲就叫「世異則事異」。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>舜</strong>做大佬嗰陣，苗族班癡線佬作反，禹想打鳩佢。<br />\n舜話：「唔得。做大佬既德行唔夠而走去打人，咁唔合符道德喎。」於是舜就修心養性三年，邀請班苗人唱歌跳舞，昆佢地話五十年不變，班苗人又真係信。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>後</strong>來禹做大佬，哩條治水癡線佬直接打鳩共工。兩邊都攞一大碌武器互插，又整定防具包實自己。唱歌跳舞happily ever after 哩一套唔會再有人信。立定架餐開片先實際。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">哩啲就叫「事異則備變」。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">上古講道德，中古講智謀，而家就直接打。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>話</strong>說齊國打魯國，魯國派孔子弟子 子貢做說客。齊人話：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你講既仁義係有道理既，<br />\n但係我而家要爭地盤，<br />\n唔係爭仁義呀，<br />\n傻西傻西傻西。<br />\n傻西傻西傻西。<br />\n傻西傻西傻西。</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>於</strong>是齊國繼續搶魯國地盤，打到去魯國都城城門既十里外先收手。<br />\nYou see ? 徐偃王行仁義所以亡國，子貢講贏齊國但係魯國都係被打。<br />\n<br />\n即係話，仁義、口才，都唔係用黎治國架。如果將偃王既仁義、子貢既口才，用黎集合徐、魯既力量打仗，咁齊國楚國就無得為所欲為啦。<br />\n<br />\n時代唔同啦，而家仲切蛋糕仲唱今天我，唔做主席唔做實事既<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">食屎啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"cb1e591000d5fb24e0033141dfde860718d1f396","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb917e45f5da5d8aa086c77dee5de54c23ea430","tid":1648414,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d005779f683f213a40af7674eeeb8778cf8a72f","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64b9af4f9ce3d203511a2cc8c8e129ec58dda3eb","tid":1648414,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"李家樹我記得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"我邊個po留過名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"應該探長post。李家樹哩個名太有料，實在係有印象"},{"pid":"55a6797d3907dc1f536ea75460556b306bacabcc","tid":1648414,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b6688575dcdeb682f72e8879cbca3125fa42c2d0","tid":1648414,"uid":332912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"巴打你譯得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c543b0971a03ffabdd93c77d3eec9751125b0c","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6688575dcdeb682f72e8879cbca3125fa42c2d0","tid":1648414,"uid":332912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"巴打你譯得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"哩位巴打真有眼光，介紹你睇個考古post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/298740/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/298740/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"45f97fb82c2dec31c19ebb57775e28fb8f025b42","tid":1648414,"uid":73392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fd5180cbe64b1cacbf4b54c4c48151e9662b025","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:56:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>【錯譯】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>是</strong>咁的。好耐之前，人少而何君堯多，人民搞唔掂班蛇蟲鼠蟻、元朗鄉親。後來有聖人出現，教民眾用木起屋避禽獸，人民服從佢既領導，推佢做王，就成為有巢氏。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>又</strong>，大家食水果蔬菜海鮮獸肉，又腥又臭又唔衛生，上吐下瀉，成日作病。又有聖人出現，教人鑽木取火BBQ，自此唔再食生肉，人民服從佢既領導，推佢做王，就成為燧人氏。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中</strong>古時候，全世界水災，鯀、禹教你疏導洪水。近古時候，夏桀、商紂癡撚線，就有商湯、周武推翻暴政。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不</strong>過，如果有巢氏喺鯀、禹既時代教鑽木取火，就實畀人笑啦。又如果有人喺商、周時代教疏導洪水，都肯定會被人恥笑。所以如果而家有人教你堯、舜、禹、湯、武既治世方法，佢肯定係傻架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所</strong>以，真正有料既人，唔會盲從以往做法，亦唔會盲從現今規範。而係會根據現時情況，因時制宜。咁先叫有料。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3ahUGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3ahUGv.png&h=1feb3fae&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<strong>有</strong>無聽過守株待兔呀？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以</strong>前宋國有個農夫，農田裡有棵樹，有隻白癡兔仔撞左落棵樹度，死左。就係咁，佢唔再耕田，日日喺棵樹隔離等兔仔撞樹，最後咪成為成語囉。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>所</strong>以你想用1989年既方法去治理今日既民眾，都係同守株待兔一樣智障架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"巴打有見識，中國兩千幾年都叫人，要效法堯舜，姐係要人用兩千幾年前嘅方法去治理，唔怪得知，中國大好條件都可以咁落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c21518431a2102dcf102f35590c48edbc6bfe8","tid":1648414,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T02:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7141e13c35fd4b6fcec384ffb4db62f692f230","tid":1648414,"uid":63328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:53:17.000Z","msg":"今日無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}